| **Component**          | **Description**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 | **Interface**                                                                                                                                                                                           |
| ---------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Linea Besu L2 Node** | Enterprise-grade Layer 2 node built on Hyperledger Besu, responsible for executing and validating smart contracts within the Linea L2 environment. It accommodates contracts such as **TokenBridge**, **ERC20/721/1155**, and **Message Contracts** to support token transfers, bridging, and interoperability. | Exposes JSON-RPC (HTTP/WebSocket) for transaction submission and contract queries; interacts with SLE Backend via Paladin Relayer; integrates with Issuer Bridge Operator for cross-network operations. |
| **Paladin Node**       | Privacy-enabled node based on Besu with additional modules for confidential transactions and private state management. It accommodates contracts such as **Noto Contract**, **NotoHookTracker**, and **Notary**, enabling private balances, event tracking, and notarization within privacy groups.             | Exposes JSON-RPC (HTTP/WebSocket) for contract calls and private transactions; provides Privacy Group APIs; accessed via Paladin SDK (used by Paladin Relayer and Issuer Bridge Operator).              |
| **Component** | **Description**                                                                                                                                                                                                  | **Interface**                                                                                                                                                                             |
| ------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Database**  | Centralized persistence layer that stores off-chain data required by the SLE system. It accommodates business records, metadata, transaction history, and any information not stored directly on the blockchain. | Exposes SQL/NoSQL queries depending on implementation (e.g., PostgreSQL, MongoDB). Interacts with the SLE DAO/Repository via JDBC/ORM. Provides read/write access to the SLE Backend API. |
